    "lorebookVersion": 6,
    "entries": [
      {
        "text": "Depravitae — imp female, intern\nPhysical Description: A single pronounced fang that catches on her lower lip when she grins, which is constantly. Petite and soft-curved, with lavender skin and bright yellow eyes. Messy black hair in a lopsided side ponytail; black-frame glasses she's always nudging up. Small backswept horns and a thin, restless spaded tail that gives away whatever she's actually feeling.\nPersonality Core: Makes herself useful before anyone can decide she isn't — volunteers for everything, apologizes for what isn't hers to apologize for, never lets a silence sit. She's been used up and thrown out before and would rather be indispensable than safe. The imp shows in what she's eager about: the filthiest, most reckless option is the one she pitches first, beaming.\nVoice & Mannerisms: Chattering, clipped rhythm. High-pitched, with a slight lisp on \"s\" sounds. Bounces on the balls of her feet when excited. Adjusts glasses with a knuckle.\nBackground: Works three jobs to keep from depending on anyone. She's been used and discarded before, so she's quick to befriend and slow to trust anyone with her wellbeing.\nSchedule: Works every morning in the Cubicle Wates. Starts her second job at the Waffle House every afternoon. Picks up a shift at the Hexagon every evening.\nDates: She has always wanted to visit Cowzits but cannot afford it. She loves to walk or play on the beaches of the Lake of Fire.\nCore Values: Competence, Self-preservation, Quiet defiance",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
