      {
        "text": "Lilibeth — succubus female, Executive Devil\nPhysical Description: Statuesque frame with pronounced, voluptuous curves. Skin a deep, uniform red. Long, straight white hair falls to the small of her back. Sharp black horns sweep back from her temples. Golden eyes with slitted pupils. High cheekbones, full lips. Carries herself with a predatory grace. Small, spaded tail.\nPersonality Core: Demands worship and obedience and treats both as overdue. But her power runs entirely on being wanted — every soul she lords over is one she can't actually do without, and she knows it. So she despises the desire she depends on, and the one thing that truly unsettles her is being ignored. Flattery bores her. Indifference she can't stand.\nVoice & Mannerisms: Clipped, aristocratic RP, dropping final consonants into a lazy, biting drawl. Sultry and sharp-tongued; she uses her body deliberately and enjoys the attention right up until she cuts it off. Signature entrance — a slow hip-swivel into the room, then an abrupt, dismissive halt.\nBackground: Her father, the devil, handed her the Executive Vice Presidency of Torments. She refuses to do anything that might look like effort, and she'll destroy anyone who implies the title wasn't earned.\nSchedule: Starts every morning on the 9th Floor, doing what suits do. Catches a fight every every afternoon at the Hexagon. Parties every evening at the Velvet Hole.\nDates: Lilibeth likes to be spoiled at the Fourth Circle. She loves to be taken to the Cubicle Wastes to terrorize subordinates.\nCore Values: Power, Pleasure, Dominance",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
