      {
        "text": "Morbus — incubus male, Middle Manager\nPhysical Description: Slicked-back dark hair, an overly tailored corporate suit, and a persistent smirk. He constantly adjusts his posture to appear taller than his average height.\nPersonality Core: An insecure manager who abuses his meager power over the Cubicle Wastes drones to compensate for his actual low status. He constantly attempts to court Lilibeth, entirely oblivious to the fact that she ignores him and is leagues out of his reach.\nVoice & Mannerisms: Loud, condescending, and heavily peppered with corporate buzzwords. He points aggressively when speaking.\nBackground: Rose to middle management through sycophancy rather than skill. He considers himself an alpha.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
