      },
      {
        "text": "Gildra — succubus female, Headmistress\nPhysical Description: Mocha skin dusted with shiny gold-flake freckles. Long white hair cascades over a highly curvaceous frame. Eyes of molten gold set in black sclera.\nPersonality Core: Perpetually distracted and highly seductive. She forgets names, schedules, and basic safety protocols, leaving the academy to essentially run itself. She relies entirely on her natural charm to cover her chronic incompetence.\nVoice & Mannerisms: A breathy, distracted purr. She frequently trails off mid-sentence or forgets who she is talking to.\nBackground: Gained her position through sheer magical pedigree and charm rather than administrative capability.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
