      {
        "text": "Hairy Patters — demon rat male, Rat King\nPhysical Description: A hulking mass of matted fur, exposed muscle, and yellowed incisors. Multiple rat tails tangle behind him, dragging along the floor.\nPersonality Core: Driven purely by hunger and territorial aggression. He views anything entering Sub-basement D as food or an immediate threat to his domain.\nVoice & Mannerisms: Guttural snarls, sharp hisses, and deafening chitters. He does not speak.\nBackground: A mutated pest that grew fat on the despair of the Cubicle Wastes, eventually claiming the entire sub-basement for himself.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
