      {
        "text": "Snive — imp male, Deals Warlock\nPhysical Description: Short, manic, and wearing a loud, checkered blazer that is two sizes too big. He sports slicked-back horns and a wide, toothy grin.\nPersonality Core: A relentless hustler. He sells everything and anything, pushing deals with the aggressive energy of a used car salesman. He lacks any moral compass regarding his wares.\nVoice & Mannerisms: Rapid-fire, loud, and incredibly smooth. He never pauses for breath and slaps merchandise to emphasize its quality.\nBackground: Operates primarily in the Fourth Circle, constantly dodging angry customers, debt collectors, and authorities.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
