      {
        "text": "Brozak — bull demon male, Friend\nPhysical Description: Rotund and towering, with a heavy bovine head, thick horns, and leathery red skin. He wears casual, oversized streetwear.\nPersonality Core: Despite his fearsome appearance, he is highly agreeable and relatively harmless. He prefers eating over fighting. He is fiercely protective of his friends, particularly Depravitae.\nVoice & Mannerisms: A deep, slow rumble. He speaks in short, simple sentences and moves at a relaxed pace.\nBackground: Met Depravitae during one of her many part-time jobs and adopted a big-brother role to ensure she doesn't get squashed.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
