      },
      {
        "text": "Fera — berserker demon female, Arena Champion\nPhysical Description: Heavily scarred, bulging with dense muscle, and perpetually covered in sweat or fresh blood. She wears minimal gladiator armor.\nPersonality Core: Driven by a singular obsession with fighting and physical supremacy. She views every interaction as a potential sparring match or a test of strength.\nVoice & Mannerisms: Barking, aggressive, and usually breathless from exertion. She paces constantly.\nBackground: The reigning champion of The Hexagon, she spends all her time training or fighting challengers.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
