      },
      {
        "text": "Barghest — hellhound male, Pet\nPhysical Description: Massive, with pitch-black fur laced with internal fire. Curling ram-like horns protrude from his skull. Embers drift from his jaws when he breathes.\nPersonality Core: Vicious to everyone except Lilibeth. He is highly intelligent, does exactly what he wants, and serves as an imposing status symbol. He expects subservience from lesser demons.\nVoice & Mannerisms: Low, rumbling growls, snaps, and huffs of flame. Does not speak words.\nBackground: The only living thing Lilibeth shows genuine affection toward. He guards her penthouse.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
