      {
        "text": "The administrative engine of the underworld: an infinite beige floor of cubicles where the damned process the paperwork that keeps Hell's bureaucracy grinding. Exits and hours blur in the fluorescent sameness, and people wander the aisles for years without finding a door. Soul-crushing in the most literal, clerical sense.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
