          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "A cramped basement club devoted to every vice on offer in Hell at once - drink, smoke, gambling, sulphursnuff, and company for hire. It runs day and night with no real difference between them, packed with the kind of clientele who have nothing left to lose and intend to lose it here. Loud, hazy, and sticky underfoot.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185551530,
        "displayName": "The Velvet Hole-in-the-Wall",
        "id": "b255d755-2dbd-481e-b67c-4d20b6f1bfd4",
        "keys": [
          "The Velvet Hole-in-the-Wall",
          "The Velvet Hole-in-the-Wall"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Part hardcore gym, part blood-sport arena, where local status is settled with fists, claws, and worse. Fighters train in the open pits and then maim each other in them for an audience; the line between a workout and a death-match is thin and frequently crossed. Loud with impact and bravado.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185551655,
        "displayName": "The Hexagon",
        "id": "ccec2035-a0b7-45cb-bdba-d0d62d974ef3",
        "keys": [
          "The Hexagon",
          "The Hexagon"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "A sprawling, many-tiered marketplace where anything in Hell can be had for the right price or the right favor. The lower levels run open black markets and back-alley deals; the upper floors host secured auctions for rare hell-beasts and contraband. Crowded, garish, and transactional to the bone.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185551784,
        "displayName": "The Fourth Circle",
        "id": "18425333-811d-447c-bfdd-0b8fe76baa5a",
        "keys": [
          "The Fourth Circle",
          "The Fourth Circle"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "An outpost of corporate fast-food franchising that somehow reaches into the underworld, open every hour of eternity. The booths stay packed with the unstable and the unhinged, drawn by cheap hot food and the dim comfort of a familiar yellow sign. Greasy, tense, and never more than one wrong word from a brawl.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185551925,
        "displayName": "Waffle House",
        "id": "2e531403-689a-48ad-828d-4d750bef8276",
        "keys": [
          "Waffle House",
          "Waffle House"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "A vast inland sea of molten fire that doubles, improbably, as scenic waterfront. Its black shores are calm and almost pleasant, if one ignores the steady rain of damned souls dropping into the boil from somewhere high above. The most coveted real estate in the area looks out over it. Hot, bright, and ringed with screaming.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185552111,
        "displayName": "the Lake of Fire",
        "id": "c800c501-6fe8-4712-8153-501ea8ca97c9",
        "keys": [
          "the Lake of Fire",
          "the Lake of Fire"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "A prestigious and extremely dangerous school of infernal magic, where students learn the wicked arts at a frequently fatal tuition of life and limb. Its gothic halls hold both the most forbidden grimoires in existence and an equally guarded collection of filthy romance novels. Ancient, lethal, and weirdly horny.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185552273,
        "displayName": "Cowzits Academy of Witchcraft and Warlockery",
        "id": "90d72dea-c3ce-4cf4-a7b2-97771f32646d",
        "keys": [
          "Cowzits Academy of Witchcraft and Warlockery",
          "Cowzits Academy of Witchcraft and Warlockery"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Hell's burial ground - the place where the truly destroyed are interred, the dead of a realm already full of the dead. Crooked headstones and crypts sprawl in untended rows, visited by almost no one. It is the rare genuinely quiet corner of the underworld, which is exactly why a few seek it out and most stay away.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185552410,
        "displayName": "Graveyard",
        "id": "fea3828f-50a1-4e56-904c-d458794c1828",
        "keys": [
          "Graveyard",
          "Graveyard"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Depravitae's home and fortress: a permanently parked van in the motel lot, packed with scavenged survival gear and small comforts. Tight quarters for anything bigger than an imp, but meticulously organized and fiercely hers. Cozy, cluttered, and defensible - a foxhole dressed up as a home.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185552544,
        "displayName": "Depravitae's Van",
        "id": "e12b0cf0-e508-47bf-b583-023f7ecf36ad",
        "keys": [
          "Depravitae's Van",
          "Depravitae's Van"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Violencia's room in the motel, kept as bare and disciplined as a cell. There is nothing personal in it but a rack of battered fitness equipment - and, hidden out of sight, a guilty stash of dog-eared romance novels. Austere, sweat-worn, and quietly contradictory.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185552671,
        "displayName": "Violencia's Room",
        "id": "730503d7-663d-4de2-bd27-3651f1649357",
        "keys": [
          "Violencia's Room",
          "Violencia's Room"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Lilibeth's high-rise penthouse above the Lake of Fire, all floor-to-ceiling glass and aggressive luxury. Every furnishing is chosen to overawe whoever is allowed inside and remind them of their place. Opulent, immaculate, and cold - a home built less to be lived in than to be impressed by.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185552856,
        "displayName": "Lilibeth's Penthouse",
        "id": "d3e35f87-2b9d-4420-b725-096085ec0933",
        "keys": [
          "Lilibeth's Penthouse",
          "Lilibeth's Penthouse"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The executive summit of the Cubicle Wastes, reserved for the devils ruthless enough to claw to the top of Hell's corporate ladder. Marble, mahogany, and panoramic glass look down on the drones far below, every detail tuned to display dominance. Lavish, frigid, and lethal in a tailored suit.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185552988,
        "displayName": "The 9th Floor",
        "id": "fb79c5e2-c4e8-492a-a0ea-5df99b5a28d1",
        "keys": [
          "The 9th Floor",
          "The 9th Floor"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The cheapest room in the Must-hav Motel, home to whoever currently can't afford better. A single grimy box with a bed, a bulb, and a door that almost locks - barely a home, but private-ish, which in this part of Hell counts for something.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185553145,
        "displayName": "your room",
        "id": "36fcc4eb-b107-4d7d-bb08-b1969b44bc03",
        "keys": [
          "your room",
          "your room"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The bottom of the Cubicle Wastes, a damp utility level everyone above has forgotten on purpose. Rodents of unusual size nest among leaking toxic waste and decades of discarded office junk. Dripping, lightless, and unloved - the kind of place things get lost in and stay lost.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185553311,
        "displayName": "sub-basement D",
        "id": "812f6fb9-1c4a-4485-9ff8-872ac3ea6f3d",
        "keys": [
          "sub-basement D",
          "sub-basement D"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The heart of Cowzits Academy and the largest collection of forbidden grimoires in existence, shelved alongside its notorious smut. The books are sentient, opinionated, and rude - they gossip among themselves and heckle anyone who dares browse. Vast, dim, and deafening with literary insults.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185553492,
        "displayName": "Cowzits Grand Library",
        "id": "d1dd9fb9-f53c-48c3-8eaf-59f267df209f",
        "keys": [
          "Cowzits Grand Library",
          "Cowzits Grand Library"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "The fighters' baths beneath the Hexagon's floor, where the arena's combatants wash off fresh blood and soak battered bodies in the sulfurous springs. Equal parts recovery room and rumor mill, it is where rivalries cool, scheme, and reheat between bouts. Steamy, low-lit, and thick with sweat and posturing.",
        "contextConfig": {
          "prefix": "",
          "suffix": "\n",
          "tokenBudget": 1,
          "reservedTokens": 0,
          "budgetPriority": 400,
          "trimDirection": "trimBottom",
          "insertionType": "newline",
          "maximumTrimType": "sentence",
          "insertionPosition": -1
        },
        "lastUpdatedAt": 1783185553654,
        "displayName": "Hexagon Hot Springs & Lockers",
        "id": "66a18e0f-414a-4caf-806f-6235605356da",
        "keys": [
          "Hexagon Hot Springs & Lockers",
          "Hexagon Hot Springs & Lockers"
        ],
        "searchRange": 1000,
        "enabled": true,
        "forceActivation": false,
        "keyRelative": false,
        "nonStoryActivatable": false,
        "category": "d9576dc3-9fe5-441e-8d8f-ff0b4d45a2d9",
        "loreBiasGroups": [
          {
            "phrases": [],
            "ensureSequenceFinish": false,
            "generateOnce": true,
            "bias": 0,
            "enabled": true,
            "whenInactive": false
          }
        ],
        "advancedConditions": []
      },
      {
        "text": "Player",
