to emphasize its quality.\",\"personalityCore\":\"A relentless hustler. He sells everything and anything, pushing deals with the aggressive energy of a used car salesman. He lacks any moral compass regarding his wares.\",\"background\":\"Operates primarily in the Fourth Circle, constantly dodging angry customers, debt collectors, and authorities.\",\"customFieldValues\":{},\"coreValues\":[],\"primaryRelationship\":{\"targetName\":\"\",\"enabled\":false,\"archetype\":\"\",\"howItStarted\":\"\",\"threads\":[],\"currentStatus\":\"\",\"trajectory\":\"\",\"summary\":\"\",\"milestones\":[],\"archetypeId\":\"\",\"stageIndex\":0},\"eventHistory\":[],\"hooks\":[],\"ephemeral\":null,\"ephemeralHistory\":[],\"lastEphemeralGen\":0,\"midRange\":null,\"lastMidrangeGen\":0,\"lastArcGen\":0,\"lastHookGen\":0,\"equippedItemIds\":[],\"charResourceDefs\":[{\"id\":\"xxmp1rn0dfafdzhjd6m\",\"name\":\"Currency\",\"tag\":\"#currency\",\"type\":\"pool\",\"hasBounds\":true,\"min\":0,\"max\":9999},{\"id\":\"3mlbvlsadjc4hr5pv42\",\"name\":\"Luck\",\"tag\":\"#luck\",\"type\":\"pool\",\"hasBounds\":true,\"min\":0,\"max\":5},{\"id\":\"tvaf5gt07kfgmcqf9k6\",\"name\":\"Health\",\"tag\":\"#health\",\"type\":\"track\",\"hasBounds\":true,\"states\":[\"Dead\",\"Severely Injured\",\"Mildly Injured\",\"Healthy\"]},{\"id\":\"l3ik0b2hn3o249i1sm6\",\"name\":\"Attitude\",\"tag\":\"#attitude\",\"type\":\"track\",\"hasBounds\":true,\"states\":[\"Hostile\",\"Unfriendly\",\"Neutral\",\"Friendly\",\"Devoted\"]},{\"id\":\"peoxo1s0po2izzglybv\",\"name\":\"Stamina\",\"tag\":\"#stamina\",\"type\":\"pool\",\"hasBounds\":true,\"min\":0,\"max\":6},{\"id\":\"mr6uqe8x7oltmmjofrb\",\"name\":\"Condition\",\"tag\":\"#condition\",\"type\":\"discrete\",\"states\":[\"None\",\"drunk\",\"sick\",\"hurt\",\"bewitched—they cannot deny any request made of them\"]}],\"charResourceValues\":{\"xxmp1rn0dfafdzhjd6m\":0,\"3mlbvlsadjc4hr5pv42\":5,\"tvaf5gt07kfgmcqf9k6\":3,\"l3ik0b2hn3o249i1sm6\":2,\"peoxo1s0po2izzglybv\":6,\"mr6uqe8x7oltmmj